Five unpainted Cadian Command Squad models for Warhammer 40k, representing a human army officer and their staff. From left to right:
An officer in a long coat and cap brandishing a gyrojet revolver (which did not come with the kit), with their other hand on a holstered power sword;
A veteran carrying a bulky plasma gun and a set of high-tech binoculars, smoking a cigarette;
A radio operator with one hand on their headset and the other tapping away at a typewriter strapped to their chest, clearly relaying orders;
A standard bearer carrying the regimental colours and a chainsaw sword;
A medic with a laser rifle slung over their shoulder while clutching a bag of medical supplies and carrying a stretcher on their back.

